data.description: Welcome to this meticulously maintained one-level home featuring 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. Impeccable inside and out, this house radiates charm and tranquility. The property boasts a serene atmosphere with a gazebo, koi pond, fountain, and a graceful windmill. Inside, an additional hobby room with a convenient half bath awaits. Recent upgrades, including new cabinets, countertops, and flooring, as well as newer appliances, all completed within the past few years, enhance the home's appeal. Nestled in the desirable Lakeside area, this home enjoys a fantastic location. But what truly sets it apart is the direct ATV route access, allowing you to embark on thrilling adventures from your doorstep to the nearby sand dunes. For fishing enthusiasts, the lake is within walking distance. This property offers a perfect fusion of comfort, convenience, and outdoor recreational opportunities. It's also noteworthy that this home is situated within a quiet and welcoming 55+ community, ensuring a peaceful and pleasant living environment for those who appreciate it.
